The paper discusses the privacy and security concerns related to machine learning classifiers, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on the use of machine learning algorithms and classifiers, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
